<p>雖</p>
<p>不論 "regardless" focusses on the lack of attention paid to what does not affect the main statement.</p>
<p>無論 "regardless" is a somewhat literary version of 不論.</p>
<p>不管 "regardless" is a very informal version of 不論.</p>
<p>NOTE THAT IN GENERAL WE ARE LEAVING THE EMPTY WORDS UNTIL LATER, TO BE DONE TOGETHER WITH MA ZHEN AND LU JIANMING</p>
